item.description:
I had the same problem with Word 365 after installing Mendeley update. Here is the solution I found out, it may help other researchers.
Step 1: Open Word, then go to &ldquo;file&rdquo;-&gt;&ldquo;options&rdquo;, a new window pops out.
Step 2: Select &ldquo;Add-ins&rdquo; in the left, then select &ldquo;word add-ins&rdquo; in &ldquo;manage&rdquo; (at the bottom), and click on &ldquo;Go&rdquo;
Step 3: Click &ldquo;add&rdquo;, then select &ldquo;Mendeley 1.19.4.dotm&rdquo; from the Mendeley installation file, it may be in &ldquo;C:\Program Files (x86)\Mendeley Desktop\wordPlugin&rdquo;
